or destroyed
as well.

04:37.043 --> 04:40.947 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: There's been
another migrant
disaster in the Mediterranean.

04:40.981 --> 04:46.520 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
