04:54.327 --> 04:58.431 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: A deadly
airstrike on a
school in Syria touched off
allegations of

04:58.465 --> 05:01.368 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
