22:11.230 --> 22:13.899 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But this is not going to be the
only issue
that's here.

22:13.933 --> 22:16.035 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
We really need to look at the
bigger picture.

22:16.068 --> 22:20.773 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We need to look at -- and I also
say, let's
elect more women to office, so
we have more

22:20.806 --> 22:22.374 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
