speak with
my other Republican women, yes,
this comes

22:28.147 --> 22:30.883 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
up, but it's not the only thing
we're talking
about.

22:30.916 --> 22:34.820 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
