protect our constitutional
rights that just have not been
brought there.

22:54.473 --> 22:59.078 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
These are things that people are
having a
hard time getting into and past
because of

22:59.111 --> 23:00.212 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
the issues at hand.

23:00.246 --> 23:02.414 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They are serious, but they're
not the only
issues.

23:02.448 --> 23:05.551 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Christine
