24:18.157 --> 24:20.392 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Missy Shorey, how
do you see
this getting resolved?

24:20.426 --> 24:24.163 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MISSY SHOREY: I think the
