of you are going to be
continuing to think

25:03.402 --> 25:06.705 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
about this hard until Election
Day and beyond.

25:06.739 --> 25:07.806 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Missy Shorey, we thank you.

25:07.840 --> 25:08.707 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Christine Matthews, thank you
for joining
us.

25:08.741 --> 25:11.043 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
CHRISTINE MATTHEWS: Thank you.

25:11.076 --> 25:15.047 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: To another
political story
today.

25:15.080 --> 25:21.153 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The hacked Clinton campaign
e-mails published
by the anti-secrecy WikiLeaks
are providing

25:21.186 --> 25:25.924 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
