been dogging
Hillary Clinton for some time,
and that is

25:25.958 --> 25:31.029 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the relationship between the
charitable Clinton
Foundation and the Clinton's
personal wealth.

25:31.063 --> 25:33.766 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
To put it in all context, here's
John Yang.

25:33.799 --> 25:38.470 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Hillary Clinton has
said job one
after she and her husband left
the White House

25:38.504 --> 25:41.540 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
in 1997 was making money.

25:41.573 --> 25:43.709 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
She talked about it in a 2014
ABC News interview.

25:43.742 --> 25:48.213 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HILLARY RODHAM CLINTON (D),
Presidential Candidate:
We had no money when we got
there, and we

25:48.247 --> 25:54.653 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
struggled to, you know, piece
together the
resources for mortgages for
houses, for Chelsea's

25:54.686 --> 25:55.687 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
education.

25:55.721 --> 25:57.556 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
You know, it wasn't easy.

25:57.589 --> 26:00.859 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
First of all, we had to pay off
all our debts,
which was -- you know, you had
to make double

26:00.893 --> 26:05.864 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the money because of, obviously,
taxes, and
pay off the debt and get us
houses and take

26:05.898 --> 26:07.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
care of family members.

26:07.766 --> 26:12.271 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN YANG: Now documents and
messages in stolen
Clinton campaign e-mails suggest
the Clinton

26:12.304 --> 26:15.107 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Foundation may have been part of
that.

26:15.140 --> 26:20.045 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They're written by Doug Band, a
White House
aide to Bill Clinton, a central
figure at

26:20.078 --> 26:25.517 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the Clinton Foundation and
creator of the
annual Clinton Global Initiative
meetings.

26:25.551 --> 26:30.923 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In November 2011, he wrote a
memo describing
the intersection of his
foundation fund-raising

26:30.956 --> 26:37.095 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
efforts and his management of
President Clinton's
for-profit business
opportunities, which Band

26:37.129 --> 26:39.932 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
called Bill Clinton, Inc.

26:39.965 --> 26:45.170 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
For example, the for-profit
Laureate International
Universities, which gave the
foundation more

26:45.204 --> 26:51.009 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
than $1 million, Band called it
a foundation
relationship that evolved into a
personal

26:51.043 --> 26:55.214 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
advisory services business
relationship for
President Clinton.

26:55.247 --> 27:01.320 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Clinton made more than $17
million over five
years as a consultant and
honorary chancellor.

27:01.353 --> 27:05.958 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
UBS Wealth Management gave the
foundation
more than a half-million
dollars.

27:05.991 --> 27:11.630 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Band said his firm encouraged
UBS to invite
President Clinton to give
several paid speeches,

27:11.663 --> 27:21.306 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
which he has done, Clinton's
fees, $900,000,
or GEMS Education, which gave
$780,000.

27:21.340 --> 27:26.044 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Band said the relationship has
grown into
a business relationship for
President Clinton.

27:26.078 --> 27:31.416 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Band wrote the memo as part of
an internal
audit which began after Chelsea
Clinton accused

27:31.450 --> 27:34.853 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
