27:46.131 --> 27:51.270 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There's also evidence that the
Clinton campaign
was concerned about the
foundation's activities.

27:51.303 --> 27:57.109 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In June 2015, campaign manager
Robby Mook
wrote campaign chairman John
Podesta: "Do

27:57.142 --> 27:59.645 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
they plan to do big events next
year?

27:59.678 --> 28:03.282 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Possible for those to be smaller
and lower-key
in '16?"

28:03.315 --> 28:08.554 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Today, a Clinton campaign
spokesman wouldn't
confirm the authenticity of the
e-mails, which

28:08.587 --> 28:14.660 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
he said were hacked by the
Russian government
to influence the election by
weaponizing WikiLeaks.

28:14.693 --> 28:19.865 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
For the "PBS NewsHour," I'm John
Yang.

28:19.898 --> 28:31.543 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Now: new rules
for broadband
providers when it comes to
collecting and

28:31.577 --> 28:33.378 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
